1n/author-0zxx9ptNwfX9AYtkCUmYYQ">Ninh Tốn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%C3%AAn-Hi%E1%BA%BFu-V%E1%BA%A5n/S%E1%BA%ADu-v%C5%A9-%C4%91%E1%BA%A3-t%C3%A2n-h%C3%A0/poem-NpSB45e8jFsxlRkRV7BsDg">Sậu vũ đả tân hà - 驟雨打遍新荷</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%C3%AAn-Hi%E1%BA%BFu-V%E1%BA%A5n/author-lCIs61Hzjl6rqKSiwGq6ow">Nguyên Hiếu Vấn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Qu%C3%BD-Th%C3%ADch/Th%E1%BA%A5t-t%E1%BB%8Bch-v%E1%BB%8Bnh-Ch%E1%BB%A9c-N%E1%BB%AF/poem-VG9SHAZzR1ONKiSKXG7CEQ">Thất tịch vịnh Chức Nữ - 七夕詠織女</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Qu%C3%BD-Th%C3%ADch/author-_a5NZkjlUmxBDVuBs6LQJg">Phạm Quý Thích</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tokugawa-Mitsukuni/Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-t%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-t%C6%B0/poem-py5Vb_484Rgr_jQ_nkfQjw">Trường tương tư - 長相思</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tokugawa-Mitsukuni/author-wy3Pfe_yc9Hmd6DdVbKQfQ">Tokugawa Mitsukuni</a>)<br></div>	</div>
